{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO838901BTC1364P0D1N001324", "chronotag": "1757948419019", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "1324", "numeroOrdreDepot": "1324", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "AN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO838901BTC1364P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PIONANR5L17BTC1364", "triAmendement": "beaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaajzzzzsi", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA840809", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO847173", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Verny"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 4", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 4", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 4", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/1364.asp#D_Article_4"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"avant_A_Apres": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "numero": "8", "alineaDesignation": "Alin\u00e9a 8"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">I.&nbsp;&#x2013;&nbsp;&#x00C0;&nbsp;l&#x2019;alin&#x00E9;a&nbsp;8, substituer &#x00E0; la premi&#x00E8;re occurrence du mot&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;soit&nbsp;&#x00BB;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">les mots&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;&#x00E0; la fois&nbsp;&#x00BB;.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">II.&nbsp;&#x2013;&nbsp;En cons&#x00E9;quence, au m&#x00EA;me alin&#x00E9;a&nbsp;8, substituer &#x00E0; la seconde occurrence du mot&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;soit&nbsp;&#x00BB;</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">le mot&nbsp;:</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#x00AB;&nbsp;et&nbsp;&#x00BB;.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Le texte actuel permet l&#x2019;acc&#x00E8;s &#x00E0; l&#x2019;aide &#x00E0; mourir en cas de souffrance r&#x00E9;fractaire aux traitements ou jug&#x00E9;e insupportable par la personne, laissant ouverte la possibilit&#x00E9; que le simple ressenti subjectif d&#x2019;insupportabilit&#x00E9; suffise, m&#x00EA;me si des traitements efficaces existent.</p><p>Cet amendement vise &#x00E0; renforcer les garanties m&#x00E9;dicales et &#x00E9;thiques en rendant ces deux conditions cumulatives. Ainsi, seules les souffrances objectivement incurables (r&#x00E9;fractaires) et subjectivement insupportables peuvent ouvrir droit &#x00E0; l&#x2019;aide &#x00E0; mourir. Cela permet de mieux encadrer la proc&#x00E9;dure, d&#x2019;&#x00E9;viter les abus ou les interpr&#x00E9;tations trop larges, et de pr&#x00E9;server la vocation ultime du dispositif : r&#x00E9;pondre &#x00E0; des situations m&#x00E9;dicales extr&#x00EA;mes, en fin de vie.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2025-05-09", "datePublication": "2025-05-19", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Rejet\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2025-05-19T17:57:01+02:00", "sort": "Rejet\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO838901BTC1364P0D1N001324?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": "RUANR5L17S2025IDS29389", "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "1", "divisionCodeLoi": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "discussionCommune": {"idDiscussion": "30868", "typePosition": "Milieu"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}